{"root":{"data":{"id":"dbdx9z0lmkw0","created":1752714050354,"text":"网络编程"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbdxc1tpprs0","created":1752714213197,"text":"系统api"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf5vqlll000","created":1752839884881,"text":"windows"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf5wx503qw0","created":1752839977479,"text":"winsocks"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf5x2arxg00","created":1752839988712,"text":"winhttp"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbf5xfsz8v40","created":1752840018111,"text":"unix"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf5xj2qqrc0","created":1752840025231,"text":"posix"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbdxceyl5lk0","created":1752714241790,"text":"三方库/框架"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbf5yakucj40","created":1752840085099,"text":"c/c++"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbdxero00f40","created":1752714426176,"text":"常见问题及解决方案"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbe0if2le7c0","created":1752723175547,"text":"网络基础"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbe0ijyij9s0","created":1752723186184,"text":"OSI七层/TCP四层"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbe0j0t3n600","created":1752723222862,"text":"应用层"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbe0j48zr7k0","created":1752723230353,"text":"http/https"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbj9vbafl9c0","created":1753257375877,"text":"版本演进","expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbj9vesmcmo0","created":1753257383450,"text":"http/0.9","note":"## 单行协议\n\n- 请求由单行指令构成\n- 请求只有 `GET` 方法，\n- 响应只包含文档本身，无响应头，只能传输html文件"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbj9vlzjs5k0","created":1753257399107,"text":"http/1.0","note":"## 可扩展的第一个版本\n\n1991-1995：开始出现\n1996：RFC 1945\n\n- 开始出现版本信息，追加到GET行\n- 出现响应状态码\n- 引入HTTP标头（请求头/响应头），提升可扩展性\n- 借助标头中的Content-Type，具备传输HTML之外的类型的文件"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbjvyiyqglk0","created":1753319692037,"text":"http/1.1","note":"### 1.0的标准化版本\n\n1997：1.0发布的几个月后。RFC 2068\n\n- http的第一个标准化版本\n- 连接可复用\n- 增加传输流水线技术\n- 支持response分块\n- 缓存控制机制\n- 内容协商机制：语言，编码，类型。允许使用最合适的约定进行内容交换\n- Host标头引入，服务器支持多域名\n\n\n1999：RFC 2616（第一次修订）\n-----\n\n\n2014：RFC 7230/RFC 7235（第二次修订，Http/2发布之前）\n-----\n\n"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbk5gsf00gw0","created":1753346513156,"text":"http/2","note":"### 优化性能\n\n2010：google实践性SPDY协议\n2015：正式标准化\n\n- 二进制协议，不再是文本协议，无法手动构造\n- 多路复用协议\n- 压缩重复头部信息\n- 缓存机制"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbk5guad4e80","created":1753346517229,"text":"http/3","note":"### 基于QUIC\n\n2022： RFC 9114\n\n在UDP协议上构建QUIC协议，用于代替tcp\n\nQUIC 旨在为 HTTP 连接设计更低的延迟。\n\n不同于HTTP/2基于单个TCP连接（会造成阻塞，丢包的时候）。quic构建为多个流"},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbe0mumheuw0","created":1752723522858,"text":"websocket","note":"用于实现长连接的其中一种技术：\n\n- websocket\n- sse（Server-send events）\n- LP（long-polling）"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbe0j8b3nio0","created":1752723239188,"text":"ftp"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"dbe0jig6z1k0","created":1752723261263,"text":"传输层"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dbe0jonvvnk0","created":1752723274789,"text":"tcp"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbojjd0bezk0","created":1753792450074,"text":"ssl/tls"},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"dbe0jsqnexs0","created":1752723283663,"text":"udp"},"children":[]}]}]}]}]},"template":"default","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}